ADDITIONAL NOTICES

Medical disclaimer. This software is a clinical reference calculator, not a
medical device. It is not FDA-cleared, not intended for diagnostic use, and
does not provide medical advice or clinical decisions. Any use in patient
care is at the sole discretion and professional responsibility of a licensed
clinician. The threshold summaries and interpretation bands displayed are
informational digests of the peer-reviewed literature cited in the
application and are not treatment recommendations.

